  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Race:</strong> Drow&nbsp;<br /><strong>Replaced Trait(s):</strong> Spell Resistance&nbsp;</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Some drow offer themselves to dark patrons, particularly demon lords. Drow with this racial trait apply their spell resistance only against spells with the good or healing descriptor or against spells cast by a divine spellcaster who worships a good-aligned deity. Anytime a drow with this racial trait casts a spell with the evil descriptor, the DC to resist the spell's effects increases by 2. This modifies the spell resistance racial trait.</p>",
